EXTRACTED VALUE: James Posey returned to action from the flu on Wednesday and had five points in 19 minutes.
Steve Nash played through a groin injury again on Friday, finishing an easy win over the Clippers with 16 points and 10 assists in 29 minutes.
Mike Bibby scored 16 points on 6-of-10 shooting (including four 3-pointers) with one rebound and two assists in 24 minutes on Saturday.
The Grizzlies signed PG Mike Conley to a five-year $45 million extension on Monday.
